    "description": "&quot;After a car accident and when I woke up, I fell back to the Joseon Dynasty in Korean history?!&quot;<br><br>As an ordinary person in the 21st century, you wake up in Korea, Joseon in 1592 AD, when Japan's invasion.<br>According to the original history, the Japanese Invasion of Korea in 1592, was a war in which Joseon won, but for some reason, Joseon was destined to collapse at this time.<br>The reason for this is the death of Yi Sun-sin, the legendary admiral, who saves Joseon in real history. <br>Now, you should change this fate...<br><br>If you designate an attack target, you can attack by swinging the sword in 8 directions or stabbing!<br>A realistic sword action game. You can block, avoid, and slash!<br>Let's save Joseon Dynasty and admiral Yi Sun-sin by a sword!<br><br><br><strong>Key features of the game</strong><br> - Full 3D graphics<br> - Physical collision of sword when you are fighting <br> - Input the direction of swinging the sword to attack the target you targeted<br> - The essential fun of sword fighting, such as seeing and avoiding the enemy's blade and using the sword's range to fight back",
